{"tid":2489344,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中共再度去信恐嚇法國議員 稱若訪台將以制裁作報復","createTime":"2021-04-15T01:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T02:14:40.000Z","uid":52779,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d371435cdf06978352f744d76a95c526815bac74","tid":2489344,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T01:38:43.000Z","msg":"繼早前罵法國人「瘋狗」、斥法國學者是「小流氓」，中共駐法大使盧沙野再度出言不遜，去信恐嚇參議院「台灣交流和研究小組」主席兼執政共和前進黨議員Alain Richard，表示對方若然再堅持訪問台灣，中共將會制裁他作報復。<br />\n<br />\n今次已經中共戰狼第二次去信恐嚇Alain Richard，事緣「台灣交流和研究小組」上月底召開會議，計劃今年夏天訪台，盧沙野及後去信Alain Richard，要求對方須避免透過任何官方形式與台灣接觸，有傳媒又表示，信中甚至用上「譴責」等字眼，但有傳媒指出，盧沙野今次比之前一封用字更差，皆因有恐嚇成分。<br />\n<br />\n經過盧沙野連番亂叫後，法國媒體對其風評相當負面，認為他是令「法中關係脫離軌道的外交官」，已有不少網民要求將他列作「不受歡迎」人物。早前法國外交部亦公開促請中方尊重法國三權分立，事後召見盧沙野表示不滿，㨿報盧沙野會上曾想提出台灣問題，但被對方叫停，表示想談的話要另約時間。<br />\n<br />\n縱然戰狼連番恐嚇，但法國政界似乎沒有退卻，「台灣交流和研究小組」上月27號甚至通過決議，不但表明不會推遲訪台之行，同時亦強調日後會支持台灣在國際組織中的地位。<br />\n<br />\n早前被盧沙野辱罵是「小流氓」的法國中國問題專家Antoine Bondaz亦表示，「台灣交流和研究小組」應該公開中方的恐嚇信，讓公眾好好討論信中內容。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意，由於短短3日前才爆出一單瑞典記者Jojje Olsson因為分析中共打壓H&amp;M的手法，被中共駐當地大使桂從友去信恐嚇對方收聲，否則後果自付，故法國網友討論盧沙野恐嚇信，都會提到瑞典。<br />\n<br />\n無疑地，隨着中國花上億改造的「遼寧號」慘在亳無防禦下被美軍近距離羞辱式監視、小粉紅一地玻璃心時，相信中共戰狼這類恫嚇外交將會越講越激，透過對外強硬的外交說辭，撫慰大陸的極端民族情緒，蓋過其軍事失利。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/soubrou/status/1381871137353781251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsoubrou%2Fstatus%2F1381871137353781251&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=433bf34e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsoubrou%2Fstatus%2F1381871137353781251&h=7df4a121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/soubrou/status/1381871137353781251</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AntoineBondaz/status/1381926317050986498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntoineBondaz%2Fstatus%2F1381926317050986498&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=b7857b78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAntoineBondaz%2Fstatus%2F1381926317050986498&h=d0d4db39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/AntoineBondaz/status/1381926317050986498</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LaLettreA/status/1381862220791963650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLaLettreA%2Fstatus%2F1381862220791963650&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=b9b944d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLaLettreA%2Fstatus%2F1381862220791963650&h=16584587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LaLettreA/status/1381862220791963650</a></blockquote><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/643\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKinternationalfront%2F643&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=6ce2a993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKinternationalfront/643</a>"},{"pid":"1bda89268b681b390b6e3d198281e819a69f56af","tid":2489344,"uid":334567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T01:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc724a5fdb68731bd2b666cedef7f2cbe2d089ef","tid":2489344,"uid":52779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T01:39:45.000Z","msg":"制裁作報復<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0416c2fa05f27ac50e1605ed84ce800c20e357","tid":2489344,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T01:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f